Strategic Initiatives
Strategic Initiatives
page.normal_text:
Increase the size and quality of the talent pool to support and expand Intracoastal industries that create high skill, high wage jobs and provide the region a competitive advantage in national and international markets. Enhance the capacity of the education, workforce and economic development systems to meet the needs of the Intracoastal industries and its workers. Catalyze innovation and foster an entrepreneurial climate for business creation and expansion.
